Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可有几分愠恼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.19,0:00:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}若是只让富贵人家享用的高级蔬菜涨价
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也无可厚非
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但竟令价格低廉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.27,0:00:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}庶民所食的豆芽菜同受牵连
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.69,0:00:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到底是何用心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.21,0:00:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}豆芽菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.47,0:00:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个…你就算问我们这些也无济于事啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.97,0:00:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}问您呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等…斑鸠同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.30,0:00:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们是严禁与外部人士接触的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.52,0:00:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是…那个人大概是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.15,0:00:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊 您到底是要无视我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.58,0:00:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord4}忍者结界！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.41,0:00:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者结界！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.70,0:00:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.18,0:00:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}硬要说来 恐怕因为您是财阀的大小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你这话是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:01:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您大概是受尽双亲宠爱 娇生惯养至今吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.58,0:01:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自自在在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.62,0:01:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恬不知耻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.05,0:01:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}生活便利毫无不适
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.68,0:01:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠同学
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.97,0:01:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟同学你先退后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.83,0:01:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.03,0:01:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这位小姐的目标看来是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.33,0:01:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\c&H250ECE&\3c&HFFFFFF&\bord4}忍·转身
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.72,0:01:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}溅落到身上的火星必须趁早扑灭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\bord4\3c&H1C3144&}忍舞参上
Comment: 0,0:01:29.93,0:01:30.11,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,OP校準幀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.35,0:01:37.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}消えない鎖 その手で壊して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:56.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}惑いに侵されて 心に潜めてた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:59.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}傷だらけの　錆びた刃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:01.46,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}闇雲に翳した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:06.76,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}弱さ認めぬまま 強くはなれないと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:09.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}知った日から　目覚め出した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:11.85,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}確かな熱に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:17.02,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}螺旋の様に 絡まる紅い罠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:24.59,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}REALを焼き付けて 彼方へ蹴散ちせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.59,0:02:30.09,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}遥かな宙に　一瞬の閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:32.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}今 亂れ咲き　影を纏い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:35.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}朧雲に放て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.90,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}信じる道は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:43.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}必ずこの手で切り拓くと誓い立てて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:48.57,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}見えない鎖 撃ち抜けmaze
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:51.29,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}You DON’T need to grieve anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.29,0:02:53.90,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Who can read the future? Know thyself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.90,0:02:56.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Ready now! Discern truth or false
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.36,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Break your world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.35,0:01:37.21,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}几重枷锁 手中破
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:56.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}困惑侵扰 心中隐匿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.38,0:01:59.00,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}斑驳疮痍 刀刃发锈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.00,0:02:01.46,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}却为暗云罩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.46,0:02:06.76,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}不堪羸弱 誓要更强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.76,0:02:09.43,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}自知起 更醒悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.43,0:02:11.85,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}热忱之切实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.85,0:02:17.02,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}庞若螺旋 赤罠笼络
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.02,0:02:24.42,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}铭刻现实 掷向彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:30.11,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}远空迢遥 一瞬閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.12,0:02:32.95,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}绮丽绽放 犹纏暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.95,0:02:35.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}耀于朧云上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.38,0:02:37.90,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}所坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:43.51,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}誓以我手 开辟我路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:48.66,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}击穿那道 无形枷锁
