Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.55,0:03:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\bord4\c&HDE8EED&\3c&HFFFFFF&}熏衣草之烂漫
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.99,0:03:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.05,0:03:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是何等怪力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.88,0:03:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您这般优雅的攻击 恐怕是伤不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.01,0:03:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\c&HDE8EED&\bord4\3c&HFFFFFF&}玫瑰的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.23,0:03:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}觉悟吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\bord4\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H16700F&}「秘传忍法•尼福尔海姆」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.90,0:03:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\bord4\3c&HFFFFFF&\c&H16700F&}{\fs40\pos(735,650)}Niflheim
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在忍转身之后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.83,0:03:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者装束会依据忍者自身的心愿以及性格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以各式各样的姿态现身
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.74,0:03:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}若是受到了物理及精神上的巨大伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.57,0:03:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}则会导致装束的损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甚至解除
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:03:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.84,0:04:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}竟然连…使用秘传忍法的余力都没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所谓善忍 也不过如此啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.86,0:04:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这么说 你果然是恶忍之人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.24,0:04:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们为何盯上我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您这居高临下的口气
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.20,0:04:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真令我愈加不快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也罢 今日就算是问候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请尽情品尝昂贵的食材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.68,0:04:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}享受须臾的人生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.24,0:04:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠同学 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没什么大碍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.36,0:04:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只能…束手旁观…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.80,0:04:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难得为半藏大人举办欢迎会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.71,0:04:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这回可真是豁出钱来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.42,0:04:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幸好最后还是控制在了预算之内
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.69,0:04:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}接下来就看我大展身手了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个…刚才的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么会知道斑鸠同学是有钱人家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}若是忍者 只要她想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}马上就能查到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.01,0:05:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}更何况斑鸠同学家里还是超级有名的财阀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}走快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等我啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.21,0:05:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}万分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我打破了您的教训
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}擅自与外部人士接触
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.22,0:05:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我愿意接受任何处罚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是对方找的茬
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.59,0:05:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别在意
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.57,0:05:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 触犯禁令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.96,0:05:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是忍者最不应当犯下的错误
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你这人还是这么顽固啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.73,0:05:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雾夜老师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.01,0:05:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您这么手下留情 如何肃立纪律
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请老师处罚我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.85,0:05:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们的话我听明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.31,0:05:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半藏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.39,0:05:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雾夜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这作为忍者的使命感是极好的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.28,0:05:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是 半藏大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.40,0:06:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然如此 就由我来处罚斑鸠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.52,0:06:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半藏大人您亲自…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}处罚？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.52,0:06:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}再动得激烈一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:20.81,Chapter,,0,0,0,,{\pos(881,559)\fad(1000,700)\bord2\blur5\3c&H001834&\1a&HFF}月下的入侵者
Dialogue: 1,0:06:16.43,0:06:20.81,Chapter,,0,0,0,,{\pos(880,558)\fad(1000,700)\c&HE3EFED&}月下的入侵者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.78,0:06:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很好…斑鸠…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半藏大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.31,0:06:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好硬啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是上了年纪啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是那儿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.91,0:06:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就是半藏大人的处罚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.49,0:06:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爷爷你这是在让斑鸠同学做些什么呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.46,0:06:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是斑鸠所希望的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 就那就那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.16,0:06:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠 我来代替你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.89,0:06:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}话说…爷爷在家里也老让我这么按
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}久违地看到这么一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.11,0:06:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}自己就也想来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.83,0:07:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样真是不禁让我想起过去在家的日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.79,0:07:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的按摩还是那么蛮横累人啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.29,0:07:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}少抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这可是你可爱孙女的按摩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.22,0:07:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好疼好疼好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.64,0:07:21.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就算是传说之忍 半藏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也拿自己孙女没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.36,0:07:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那两位真是一家人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.52,0:07:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}废话 当然是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.90,0:07:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱歉 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}发生什么事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.51,0:07:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}刚刚从斑鸠家里来了消息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.97,0:07:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠家？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.66,0:07:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}袭击你们的恶忍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是个怎样的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.57,0:07:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个…飘飘然的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那算啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.63,0:07:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然后 她身手很了得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我完全不知所措的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是没有斑鸠同学在…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠同学 真的很对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.52,0:08:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用在意 是我指示你退后的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊 是斑鸠把她收拾了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.22,0:08:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可恶 咱家也想参一脚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.04,0:08:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只不过没把她当一回事罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.65,0:08:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者必须避开不必要的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}切 咱家可会认真地修理他们一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}像这样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.18,0:08:25.94,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}干嘛啊你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.06,0:08:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其实只是束手无策罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.93,0:08:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我斑鸠…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.63,0:08:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.30,0:08:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.55,0:08:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.10,0:08:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.12,0:08:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们俩关系真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.79,0:08:48.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对吧 小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.61,0:08:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只是看云雀容易受危险
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.89,0:08:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想保护她罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你又把人家当小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.68,0:08:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}关系♀好可是件美事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.81,0:09:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对了 还会一起去洗澡来着？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.26,0:09:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}互相洗澡澡冲冲背
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.86,0:09:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真好啊 啥时候也叫上老朽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别跟她们说些奇怪的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.66,0:09:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是啦 飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.10,0:09:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我这是在交流感情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.47,0:09:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不愧是半藏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.02,0:09:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}兄长大人失踪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从你老家来的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.14,0:09:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}保险起见 想问问你有什么头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}即使是向我这么问起 我也毫无头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.50,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}毕竟我与兄长交谈甚少
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.83,0:09:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.34,0:09:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.27,0:09:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只是保险起见 想知会你一声罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么说也是你家人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.05,0:09:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}家人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.73,0:10:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有…刚才背后好像有视线…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.17,0:10:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.80,0:10:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好像是我的错觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事吧 斑鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.13,0:10:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好了 欢迎会还有三十分钟哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:21.52,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}切 不能闹到天亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.14,0:10:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大概是因为恶忍还有老师刚才的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.32,0:10:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有些过敏了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.47,0:10:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不像我啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.37,0:10:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从今天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她就是你的妹妹了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.56,0:10:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要好好相处哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.33,0:10:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请…请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.29,0:10:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸买来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.19,0:10:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}注意你的言辞 村雨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.80,0:10:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她是我们远房亲戚家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.73,0:10:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎样都好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.72,0:10:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸要丢下我 也得找个替代品嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你说够了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.70,0:11:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不用介意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.25,0:11:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}即便是亲生骨肉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有时也得大义灭亲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.61,0:11:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那便是忍者的守则
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.76,0:11:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞燕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.80,0:11:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是我们家门代代相传的名刀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.61,0:11:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把你视作我的女儿 将它传予你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是 父亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.60,0:11:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为了代替缺乏忍者才能的财阀家长子 村雨
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.39,0:11:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而被财阀收做了养女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.68,0:11:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为何要离家出走呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是谁！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哟哟 可真凶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.06,0:12:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}兄长大人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好久不见啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}兄长大人 你为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.59,0:12:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要那么叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.48,0:12:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可没有什么妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.57,0:12:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要拿飞燕做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.26,0:12:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做什么？这本来就是我的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.81,0:12:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要做什么都是我的自由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.74,0:12:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.93,0:12:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那把飞燕是我从父亲大人那里…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}父亲大人？你叫得还真是自在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.65,0:12:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真把我们当一家人了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.90,0:12:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}确实我还用不惯这玩意儿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.61,0:12:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但这可是我们家传的宝刀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.03,0:12:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是给你这种非亲非故的外人拿的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.47,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞燕是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.07,0:13:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本该就是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.31,0:13:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是没有…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.89,0:13:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是没有你在！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我真的感到非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.00,0:13:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你若是恨我 我愿意道歉到你满意为止
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.16,0:13:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想戏弄我到什么地步！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只是想要你把飞燕归还于我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那你就来拿看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.19,0:13:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}该死！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.79,0:13:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我小学的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是市里锁镰大赛的第六名啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.19,0:13:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么样！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.65,0:13:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这下你动不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.91,0:13:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拜托了 请您收手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.78,0:13:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}该死！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.95,0:13:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把我当笨蛋耍！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请当心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是绝对不会认可你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.93,0:13:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}绝对不会！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:14:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}该死 该死
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个臭婊子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.31,0:14:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我总有一天要…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.88,0:14:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的一举一动
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.15,0:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从你踏进校园起我就了如指掌了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我劝你还是老实回家经商吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.02,0:14:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你为什么知道这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}少自说自话了 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.85,0:14:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要是就此罢手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.98,0:14:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就不问不究了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的父亲这样跟我说过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}「我儿子虽然无法胜任为一个忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是他却有经商的头脑」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.22,0:14:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爸爸他……
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者并不是唯一的出路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}世上有多少人 就有多少条路
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.96,0:14:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.82,0:14:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对你来说还是不知道为好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.68,0:14:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就尽管当我是位路过的老爷子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.38,0:15:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要是认为光靠气势就能掌握招式
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.90,0:15:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那可就大错特错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.30,0:15:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.67,0:15:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀同学 你要是这么出招
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.56,0:15:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会遭人反手的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太松懈了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}脾气真大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.95,0:15:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.64,0:15:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你今天有点怪怪的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.35,0:15:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感觉战战兢兢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.14,0:15:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才没有战战兢兢的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.80,0:15:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但现在可说不准恶忍什么时候会杀过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.63,0:15:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们必须要变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.92,0:15:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你光是这么呼来喝去的也没什么用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.26,0:15:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城同学你又没有打过
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.12,0:15:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}当然说得轻巧了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.82,0:15:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你打过了就了不起了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.75,0:15:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我说的是你不够正经
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.81,0:15:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你说什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生 该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.96,0:15:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}两个人都冷静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.47,0:15:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一年级的给我闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.11,0:15:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}各位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.16,0:16:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来吃点心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:06.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}今天爷爷也给我们送慰劳品来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟用她天真的率直 将大家团结在了一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.75,0:16:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}或许真正适合当班级领队的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是飞鸟同学这样的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她为自己的事情都搞得团团转了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.27,0:16:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半藏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.34,0:16:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}您来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.89,0:16:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的 身为我的孙女还这么不成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真让人伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.65,0:16:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能带得起这帮野丫头的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.68,0:16:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然还是非斑鸠不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.72,0:16:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪里 我也不过是成日为心事所乱罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.04,0:16:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也快要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.44,0:16:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.00,0:16:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.90,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对于现在的飞鸟来说
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们就像是她的家人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}互相之间毫无芥蒂地欢笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.90,0:16:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗔骂 互相依靠 帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.44,0:16:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而现在正是这么一番景致
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.30,0:17:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}确实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.10,0:17:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们忍者班级或许真的就像一个小家庭那样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.36,0:17:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对我来说亦是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那就没什么可畏惧的了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.18,0:17:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好痒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.50,0:17:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.97,0:17:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}味道如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.03,0:17:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我做的粗卷寿司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.21,0:17:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.07,0:17:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}粗卷寿司和半藏大人我都最喜欢了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.08,0:17:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半藏大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:30.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs36}一、若是为了积累修行经验的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:30.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs36}不论是爆破、破坏或其他此类行为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:30.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs36}都予以认可。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:30.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs36}二、不论何时都要以性命为优先
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:30.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs36}三、不论何时何、都要遵守身为善
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:30.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs36}忍的言行举止。
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:30.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs36}四、对自己所召唤出的生物、召唤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:30.57,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs36}者必须负起责任
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.75,0:17:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你要为飞鸟进行秘传忍法的特训？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能得到许可吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.12,0:17:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个…这不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我认为里面的瀑布不错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.72,0:17:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等一下 斑鸠同学
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么要淋水啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.06,0:17:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}首先要和召唤的动物心意相通
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.95,0:17:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说到青蛙蟾蜍 那当然是水了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.30,0:17:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白了它们的感觉了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是…差不多吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.50,0:18:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小飞鸟…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.76,0:18:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她没问题吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.84,0:18:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前路漫长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.88,0:18:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}别提亲近了…就是碰它都…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是因为你心里想着怕它才会怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难得斑鸠同学你来陪我修行…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.35,0:18:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是应该的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为我们是一家人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.03,0:18:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好啦 快加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.45,0:18:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还差一点…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.75,0:18:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.55,0:18:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}连甩开它都做不到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.86,0:18:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为要是甩开了…青蛙先生多可怜啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可怜？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.45,0:18:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你想 突然把它甩开扔飞的话不是很可怜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我先去看看大家的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.29,0:19:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎 怎么这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你就把我和青蛙先生丢在这了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可怕…不可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.97,0:19:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行！果然还是很可怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.62,0:19:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}危险！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.52,0:19:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}青蛙先生它！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠同学 不要吓我啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}看来你终于能自己去碰它了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我是以为青蛙先生它…会有危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.20,0:19:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就不知不觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.53,0:19:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还觉得可怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.02,0:19:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咦 好奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.81,0:19:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说起来…感觉它…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.68,0:20:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也挺可爱的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.38,0:20:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哎…哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.04,0:20:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我本该早些注意到才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.30,0:20:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为你就是这样的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur8\bord4\3c&H16700F&}「秘传忍法•二刀缭斩」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.78,0:20:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不错
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}成功了啊 飞鸟同学
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.87,0:20:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}干得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.44,0:20:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爷爷 我做到了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.29,0:20:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯 做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.34,0:20:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是怎么让她克服对青蛙的恐惧的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.05,0:21:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟同学她 原本就是位待人接物都很温柔的人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.83,0:21:06.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她只是固执的坚信自己会害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.10,0:21:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知不觉在心里筑起了一道高墙罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以说 如果能让她自己肯去接触
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那道墙也就自然而然地消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}斑鸠果然可靠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.50,0:21:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也自叹不如吶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只是做了班长所该做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.16,0:21:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}半藏大人 非常感谢您
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.15,0:21:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你在说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.53,0:21:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}该道谢的是我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我家孙女可真是幸福吶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.11,0:21:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不仅有可爱的妹妹 还有这么位出色的姐姐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.91,0:21:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}姐姐吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.42,0:21:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}终于轮到我出场了呢
Comment: 0,0:21:55.10,0:21:55.70,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.36,0:22:16.85,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}この道で決めたから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.85,0:22:22.00,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}どこまでも迷わないの
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.75,0:22:29.02,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}前向きな情熱に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.15,0:22:34.55,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}相応しい勇気が光る
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.92,0:22:38.16,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}選んだ思いが全部
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.16,0:22:41.35,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}運命だったらいいな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.35,0:22:43.48,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}覚悟はできてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.48,0:22:46.41,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}勇ましく　誇らしく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.41,0:22:50.32,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}凛々しく進もう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.32,0:22:52.41,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}夢に今　Ready Go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:55.73,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}挑んでいくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.35,0:22:59.63,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}いつだって　真っ直ぐな
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.63,0:23:02.66,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}私が道しるべ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.66,0:23:05.13,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}毎日に　Kiss Kiss
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.57,0:23:08.15,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}恋するみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.69,0:23:12.55,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}真剣勝負が基本だよね
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:14.16,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}信じている　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:15.67,ED-JA,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(200,200)}夢に秘めた
